playstore_details.title: Eidoo: Bitcoin and Ethereum Wallet and Exchange
playstore_details.description:
Eidoo. The world of decentralized finance at your fingertips.
Eidoo is your gateway to the exciting new world of open finance.
An app designed for both your mobile and desktop devices, it’s the easiest and most secure way to explore the entire DeFi ecosystem. 
Easy to use multidimensional, multicurrency wallet
Manage, buy, store, sell, exchange or trade major cryptocurrencies and tokens. As a non-custodial wallet, funds will always remain in your full control, with effortless wallet backup and recovery options. 
Eidoo Card, your personal crypto-powered debit card
Pre-orders are now open for the Eidoo-branded debit card, linked to your non-custodial wallet. Enjoy an industry-first crypto cashback program, with up to 10% back on qualifying purchases. 
One KYC, unlimited possibilities 
Eidoo is home to your only crypto KYC. Verify your identity and set up your eidooID profile to access any of our integrated services or platforms account-free. 
Trade how you like, whenever you like
Trade your digital currencies using our Hybrid Exchange, or use our atomic swap feature and instantly swap between hundreds of possible pairs.
Exclusive access to token offerings  
Participate in, or even launch, token sales that are 100% compliant with local regulations. We list one-off opportunities to back unique projects. 
DeFi Exchange - Your gateway to DeFi
Explore the entire DeFi ecosystem and easily manage your entire portfolio. Earn interest on your digital assets, or acquire tokens with inbuilt investment strategies. Anything is possible - you’re just one swap away. 
Instant SEPA - cash in and cash out your crypto in seconds 
We’re the first decentralized wallet to offer an in-built crypto on and off-ramp feature, enabling all European users to instantly buy or sell assets using the SEPA network. What used to take days, now takes seconds. 
____
Discover the most multi-dimensional wallet industry-wide. It’s more than a wallet - it’s everything you need to explore the world of blockchain finance. 
Restrictions:
Eidoo Sagl is incorporated under the laws of Switzerland.
SUPPORT 
Contact us directly from the app by filling out our “Send us a Report” form. Leave us feedback or report your issue.
Your data is handled according to our privacy policy.
